{"text_id":189525,"tokens":["Although"," molecular"," clouds"," are"," a"," pervasive"," feature"," of"," star","-","forming"," galaxies",","," the"," mechanisms"," governing"," their"," physical"," and"," chemical"," properties"," remain"," poorly"," understood","."," In"," this"," study",","," we"," compare"," the"," anomalous"," ","6","-","cm"," H","$_","2","$","CO"," absorption"," and"," CO","(","1","-","0",")"," emission"," in"," the"," L","1","2","0","4"," and"," S","1","4","0"," regions"," of"," the"," Cy","gnus"," X"," molecular"," cloud","."," This"," comparison"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," the"," relationship"," between"," dense"," gas"," and"," the"," surrounding"," interstellar"," radiation"," field","."," We"," employ"," a"," combination"," of"," single","-","dish"," and"," interfer","ometric"," observations"," to"," measure"," the"," spectral","-","line"," intensities"," and"," spatial"," distributions"," of"," H","$_","2","$","CO"," and"," CO","."," Our"," results"," indicate"," that"," the"," anomalous"," ","6","-","cm"," H","$_","2","$","CO"," absorption"," is"," strongly"," associated"," with"," the"," presence"," of"," CO","(","1","-","0",")"," emission",","," suggesting"," that"," both"," species"," are"," tracing"," the"," same"," dense"," and"," cold"," gas","."," The"," observed"," correlation"," between"," the"," two"," species"," suggests"," that"," the"," anomalous"," ","6","-","cm"," H","$_","2","$","CO"," absorption"," is"," not"," solely"," due"," to"," optical"," depth"," effects"," or"," background"," radiation",","," but"," rather"," is"," a"," result"," of"," a"," complex"," interplay"," between"," gas"," and"," radiation","."," Our"," findings"," have"," important"," implications"," for"," the"," understanding"," of"," molecular"," cloud"," chemistry"," and"," the"," interstellar"," radiation"," field",","," and"," highlight"," the"," potential"," of"," combining"," anomalous"," absorption"," and"," emission"," observations"," to"," probe"," the"," physical"," and"," chemical"," properties"," of"," these"," complex"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}